  "metadata": {
    "name": "Ensure All User Initialization Files Have Mode 0740 Or Less Permissive",
    "description": "Set the mode of the user initialization files to <tt>0740</tt> with the\nfollowing command:\n<pre>$ sudo chmod 0740 /home/<i>USER</i>/.<i>INIT_FILE</i></pre>",
    "rationale": "Local initialization files are used to configure the user's shell environment\nupon logon. Malicious modification of these files could compromise accounts upon\nlogon.",
